Feature: User places the order

  Scenario: Placing the order
    Given Navigates to to login page
    When The user inputs the email
    And The user inputs the password
    And The user clicks Sign In button
    And The user clicks on Women section
    And The user clicks on the product's button
    And The user selects the product's size
    And The user clicks  Add to the cart button
    And The user clicks  Proceed to check out button
    And The user clicks  Proceed to check out button again
    And The user clicks  Confirm address button
    And The user clicks  Confirm delivery option button
    And The user selects payment type
    And The user accepts agreement
    And The user clicks  Submit button
    Then YOUR ORDER IS CONFIRMED message shows up